{% extends "AppBundle:Haunted/Comic:comics_layout.html.twig" %}
{% block title %}사립 다이스스쿨 8교시!{% endblock %}
{% block comicContents %}
    <span class="bold size24">사립 다이스스쿨 제 8교시</span>
    <div><img id="comics" src="{{asset("bundles/app/image/haunted/diceschool/diceschool_008.jpg")}}"></div>
    <div id="comment">
        <span class="bold">모든것을 잃어버린 이윤주 :</span>
        <span>(읍컥)</span><br>
        <span class="bold">폭발사산 채미리 :</span>
